item.content:encoded:

item.content:encoded:

item.description: Chain Cubes 2048 is a free casual merging puzzle online game. The Cubes don’t stay in place, they pop out. If you fail to merge the cube number blocks, they will bounce off each other! Shoot and hit the number blocks with the same color and number. Combine the number blocks and bounce to merge […]
item.content:encoded:
Chain Cubes 2048 is a free casual merging puzzle online game. The Cubes don’t stay in place, they pop out. If you fail to merge the cube number blocks, they will bounce off each other! Shoot and hit the number blocks with the same color and number. Combine the number blocks and bounce to merge the cubes to get new number blocks.
On PCSlide the block to play.On MobileSlide the block to play.
